headline: Prologis to Participate in BofA Securities 2025 Global Real Estate Conference
summary: Prologis, Inc. (NYSE: PLD) today announced that Tim Arndt, chief financial officer, will present at the BofA Securities 2025 Global Real Estate Conference in New York, NY on Wednesday, September 10, at 9:35 a.m. ET.
